name: Raycasting WH4RD
description:
Raycasting WH4RD is generated with a ray-casting algorithm with random placement of lights and boundaries. The artwork reveals interesting Moiré effects and interleaved perspectives.

PNG, 2000 × 2000 PNG

Generative artwork by Gwenaël Le Bodic
